overview.en: The origin of Birdcoin was due to a disgruntled KOL who disapproved of Sun Ge's actions. On July 24, 2023, he saw Sun Ge's tweet praising CZ, so he soulfully questioned Sun Ge:

CZ responded with a 🦜, causing laughter. Following suggestions from followers, Birdcoin was established, and 100% of the coins were airdropped to the community for free via Twitter. Philosophy: purity, freedom, equality, and universal love.
overview.cn: 鸟币起源是因为某个愤青kol看不惯孙割的做法，2023年7月24日他看到孙割推特发了一篇拍CZ马屁的推文，于是他向孙割发出灵魂拷问：你看CZ鸟你不？CZ含笑评论了他一个🦜，众人哄笑，在推友的建议下，鸟币成立，100%的鸟币都通过推特免费空投给了社区。理念：纯净，自由，平等，博爱
